要連續三十三日才能見哂怒睥佢既人。除非佢盡快匿返狗屋。<br />\n<br />\n所以一人一怒睥，根據黃子華講法，舔都舔死佢，<br />\n依家係，睥都啤死佢。<br />\n<br />\np.s. 不科學的approximation"},{"pid":"2cc88ab8e22c5f94c8b6a9d324e4940b4842e2c5","tid":1325331,"uid":269533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUEBEy2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUEBEy2.png&h=a10ccdea&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}